        <ul>
            <li>
                Clone this repository:
                <ul>
                    <li>git clone git@github.com:JohnDeere/MyJohnDeereAPI-OAuth2-CSharp-Example.git</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Build the project:
                <ul>
                    <li>Build Solution</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            <li>
                Start it:
                <ul>
                    <li>Run IIS Express</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>











    </p>
